al data analysis skills. Perfect for learners with a problem-solving mindset who want to apply analytical thinking to real-world AI challenges and intelligent agent development.", "included_items": "Instructor-led OR Self-paced course + Official exam + Digital badge", "certificate_duration": "<ul>\\n<li>Instructor-Led: 1 day (live or virtual)</li>\\n<li>Self-Paced: 8 hours of content</li>\\n</ul>\\n"}, "certification_modules": [{"certification_module_title": "Module 1: Introduction to AI Agents", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1.1 Understanding AI Agents</li>\\n<li>1.2 Anatomy and Ecosystem of AI Agents</li>\\n<li>1.3 Applications, Misconceptions, and Mini Case Studies</li>\\n<li>1.4 Case Study: Transforming Customer Support at Acme Retail with AI Agents</li>\\n<li>1.5 Hands-On Exercise 1: Build a Q&amp;A ChatBot Using Gemini + Prompt + LLM Chain in Flowise Cloud</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: Core Concepts & Types of AI Agents", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>2.1 Anatomy of an AI Agent</li>\\n<li>2.2 Classification of AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2.3 Matching Agents to Use Cases</li>\\n<li>2.4 Case Study: Enhancing Mental Health Support with AI Agents at Earkick</li>\\n<li>2.5 Hands-On Exercise</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: Tools for Non-Coders", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>3.1 No-code and visual agent platforms</li>\\n<li>3.2 Tools Overview and Setup</li>\\n<li>3.3 Start building: “Your First Flow” with n8n</li>\\n<li>3.4 Case Study: Empowering HR with AI – Building an Onboarding Assistant Without Coding</li>\\n<li>3.5 Hands-on Exercise</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: Building Simple Agents", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 Agent 1</li>\\n<li>4.2 Agent 2</li>\\n<li>4.3 Agent 3</li>\\n<li>4.4 Agent 4</li>\\n<li>4.5 Troubleshooting and Validation of AI Agents</li>\\n<li>4.6 Share Your AI Agent</li>\\n<li>4.7 Hands-On Exercise 1</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Multi-Tool Agents and Workflow Automation", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Multi-Tool Agents</li>\\n<li>5.2 Agent Chaining and Workflow Basics</li>\\n<li>5.3 Managing Agent State: State, Context, and User Journey</li>\\n<li>5.4 Prompt Engineering for Agents</li>\\n<li>5.5 Multi-Agent Systems (MAS)</li>\\n<li>5.6 Case Study: Smarter Marketing Campaigns with Tool Chaining</li>\\n<li>5.7 Hands-on Exercise: Automating Order Tracking and Notifications with Make.com</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Integration, Application Mapping & Deployment", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Deploying Agents</li>\\n<li>6.2 Channel Selection – Where the User will Interact</li>\\n<li>6.3 Hosting Environment – Where does the Agent Run?</li>\\n<li>6.4 Data Integration</li>\\n<li>6.5 Security Setup</li>\\n<li>6.6 Monitoring &amp; Updates</li>\\n<li>6.7 Application Mapping</li>\\n<li>6.8 Hands-on Exercise 1: Integration of a Portfolio Assistant Chatbot into GitHub Pages using Zapier</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Monitoring, Guardrails & Responsible AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Observability Basics</li>\\n<li>7.2 Performance Evaluation: Key Metrics</li>\\n<li>7.3 Guardrails: Preventing Misuse &amp; Ensuring Safe Outputs</li>\\n<li>7.4 Responsible AI</li>\\n<li>7.5 Mini-Case: Failure and Recovery in Agent Deployments</li>\\n<li>7.6 Real-world Failures</li>\\n<li>7.7 Peer Sharing: How to Present and Discuss Agent Logs/Results</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Capstone Project – Design Your Own Intelligent Agent", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Capstone Project 1: Smart Personal AI Assistant</li>\\n<li>8.2 Capstone Project 2: Smart Lead Engagement &#8211; From Email to Personalized Outreach &#8211; Sales Support Agent</li>\\n<li>8.3 Capstone Project 3: Education Tutor Agent</li>\\n<li>8.4 HR Knowledge Bot</li>\\n<li>8.5 Customer Service Agent</li>\\n<li>8.6 Healthcare Triage Bot</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAIC_AI-Agent.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Aspiring AI Professionals:</strong> Learners looking to break into AI by building practical experience with intelligent agents and automation.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Software Developers &amp; Engineers:</strong> Python or similar language programmers who want to design, integrate, and deploy AI agents into real applications.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Data Analysts &amp; Data Scientists:</strong> Professionals who work with data and want to operationalize insights through AI-driven agents and workflows.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Product Managers &amp; Tech Leaders: </strong>Decision-makers aiming to understand, plan, and oversee AI agent solutions that enhance products and services.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Automation &amp; Operations Specialists:</strong> Those focused on process optimization who want to replace repetitive tasks with smart, autonomous AI agents.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Industry Recognition:", "key_points_detail": "A specialized credential that signals strong capability in AI agent design, deployment, and management."}, {"key_points": "Career Differentiation:", "key_points_detail": "A standout addition to your profile that highlights expertise in AI-powered automation and intelligent workflows."}, {"key_points": "Hands-on Proficiency:", "key_points_detail": "Demonstrated experience using agent-building tools, frameworks, and best practices to solve real problems."}, {"key_points": "Business Value Creation:", "key_points_detail": "Proven ability to build agents that streamline operations, elevate customer experiences, and drive measurable ROI."}, {"key_points": "Future-ready Skill Set: ", "key_points_detail": "Strong alignment with the growing demand for AI agents across industries, keeping your skills relevant and competitive."}]}, "lms_course_id": "796", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AIC_AI-Agent.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AIC_AI-Agent.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:44:34.278927+02	2026-01-23 07:44:25.331633+02	2026-04-27 10:44:34.280875+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAIC_AI-Agent.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAIC_AI-Agent.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "Python", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Python.png"}, {"name": "LangChain", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/langchain-2.png"}, {"name": "LlamaIndex", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/LlamaIndex.png"}, {"name": "OpenAI API", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/OpenAI-AP.png"}, {"name": "Hugging Face Inference", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Hugging-Face-Transformers-for-Biomedical-NLP.png"}, {"name": "Multi-Agent Orchestration Frameworks", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Multi-Agent-Orchestration-Frameworks.png"}, {"name": "Vector Databases (e.g., Pinecone, Chroma)", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Vector-Databases.png"}, {"name": "Workflow Orchestration (e.g., Airflow, Prefect)", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Workflow-Orchestration.png"}, {"name": "Jupyter Notebooks", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jupyter.jpg"}, {"name": "Docker", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.