"https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AIC_AI-Program-Director-Practitioner.svg", "certificate_overview": {"exam_format": "50 questions, 70% passing, 90 minutes, online proctored exam", "prerequisites": "A good understanding of AI/ML fundamentals, project management experience, business strategy knowledge, familiarity with governance and compliance, and strong leadership and change management skills are essential for this course.", "included_items": "Instructor-led OR Self-paced course + Official exam + Digital badge", "certificate_duration": "<ul>\\n<li>Instructor-Led: 5 days (live or virtual)</li>\\n<li>Self-Paced: 40 hours of content</li>\\n</ul>\\n"}, "certification_modules": [{"certification_module_title": "Module 1: Foundations of AI for Program Strategy – Introduction", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1.1 Understanding of AI, ML, and Deep Learning</li>\\n<li>1.2 AI Lifecycle &amp; Real-World Applications</li>\\n<li>1.3 Societal Impact of AI</li>\\n<li>1.4 Use Case: Triage System (AI for Emergency Services)</li>\\n<li>1.5 Case Study: Retail Recommendation System (Personalizing Customer Experience)</li>\\n<li>1.6 Hands-on: Use Teachable Machine to Build a Simple AI Classifier</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: Identifying AI Opportunities & Use Cases ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>2.1 Introduce AI Strategy Alignment Frameworks: AI Canvas, Value vs Feasibility Matrix</li>\\n<li>2.2 Signs That a Process May Benefit from AI: Repetitive Tasks, Data-Rich Environments, Personalization Needs</li>\\n<li>2.3 Prioritization Techniques: Weighted Scoring, Risk-Adjusted ROI</li>\\n<li>2.4 Use-Case: Financial AI – Fraud Detection Systems Using AI</li>\\n<li>2.5 Case Study: AI-Driven Project Management System for a Program Director</li>\\n<li>2.6 Hands-on: Use Trello to Create a Board and Prioritize AI Opportunities Within a Given Scenario</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: Governance & Ethics in AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>3.1 Responsible AI Principles</li>\\n<li>3.2 AI Bias &amp; Risk Mitigation</li>\\n<li>3.3 Use-case: Auditing Bias in AI-Powered Recruitment to Ensure Fair Hiring</li>\\n<li>3.4 Case Study: Mitigating Algorithmic Bias in Credit Scoring Models to Ensure Fair Lending Practices</li>\\n<li>3.5 Hands-on: Use Google’s What-If Tool in Google Colab to Evaluate Model Fairness and Bias</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: AI Project Lifecycle & Integration ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 AI Project Planning &amp; CRISP-DM</li>\\n<li>4.2 Integration: Build vs Buy vs Partner</li>\\n<li>4.3 AI Project Management Tools</li>\\n<li>4.4 Use Cases: AI for Predictive Maintenance (Asset Management in Manufacturing)</li>\\n<li>4.5 Tool-Based Hands-on Activity: Simulate an AI Project in Asana</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Data Strategy & Infrastructure for AI ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Data Governance &amp; Quality</li>\\n<li>5.2 Setting up Data Pipelines for AI</li>\\n<li>5.3 Sensitive Data Management</li>\\n<li>5.4 Use Case: Retail Inventory System — AI-driven Restocking and Demand Prediction</li>\\n<li>5.5 Case Study: Healthcare Data Security — Managing Patient Privacy in AI-Based Healthcare Systems</li>\\n<li>5.6 Tool-Based Hands-on Activity: Set up Airbyte Cloud and Build a Basic Data Pipeline</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: AI Integration — Build vs Buy vs Partner ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Evaluating AI Solutions</li>\\n<li>6.2 Vendor Evaluation &amp; Management</li>\\n<li>6.3 Use Case: AI Vendor Selection — Choosing Predictive Maintenance Solutions for a Manufacturing Plant</li>\\n<li>6.4 Tool-Based Hands-on Activity: Use a Vendor Selection Template to Evaluate AI Vendors (Google Sheets)</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: AI Risk Management & Compliance ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Regulatory Frameworks</li>\\n<li>7.2 Bias Detection &amp; Mitigation</li>\\n<li>7.3 Use Case: Facial Recognition Bias (Law Enforcement Systems)</li>\\n<li>7.4 Case Study: AI in Finance: Ensuring Compliance in AI Deployments</li>\\n<li>7.5 Tool-Based Hands-on Activity: Bias Testing &amp; Fairness Evaluation Using KNIME and Google PAIR Facets Fairness Explorer</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: AI Tools & Techniques for Project Management ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 AI Project Management Tools</li>\\n<li>8.2 Data Management Tools</li>\\n<li>8.3 Case Study and Use Case: AI Workflow Management: Using project management tools for AI deployment in the retail sector</li>\\n<li>8.4 Tool-Based Hands-on Activity: Use Asana to simulate project timelines, setting up tasks and milestones for an AI initiative</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 9: Leadership in AI ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>9.1 Leading AI Teams &amp; Change Management</li>\\n<li>9.2 Managing Stakeholders &amp; Communication</li>\\n<li>9.3 Use Case: AI in Manufacturing: Leading AI Implementation in a Large-Scale Manufacturing Operation</li>\\n<li>9.4 Tool-Based Hands-on Activity: Use Miro to Map Stakeholder Communication Strategies and Identify Key Influencers</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 10: Scaling AI Initiatives ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>10.1 From Pilot to Full-Scale Deployment</li>\\n<li>10.2 Organizational Maturity Models for AI</li>\\n<li>10.3 Use Case: Scaling AI in Retail: Expanding AI-driven Recommendations Globally</li>\\n<li>10.4 Tool-Based Hands-on Activity: Create a Scaling Roadmap Using Lucidchart Outlining Key steps in Scaling AI Initiatives.</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 11: Future Trends in AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>11.1 Emerging AI Technologies</li>\\n<li>11.2 Use Case / Case Study: AI in Autonomous Vehicles: The future of AI in self-driving cars</li>\\n<li>11.3 Tool-Based Hands-on Activity: Explore Hugging Face Transformers for NLP and TensorFlow for Deep Learning Applications</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 12: Capstone Project & Presentation ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>12.1 Capstone Project Overview</li>\\n<li>12.2 Presentation &amp; Feedback</li>\\n<li>12.3 Final Review &amp; Certification – Method, Process, and Feedback Mechanism</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAIC_AI-Program-Director-Practitioner.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>AI Project Managers: </strong>Ideal for project managers looking to lead AI initiatives and ensure successful implementation across organizations.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Business Leaders: </strong>For executives and managers aiming to integrate AI into business strategies and drive operational efficiency.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Program Directors: </strong>Designed for program directors who want to master AI project management and lead cross-functional AI teams.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>AI Professionals: </strong>For AI specialists seeking to enhance their leadership skills and move into strategic program management roles.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Change Managers: </strong>Great for professionals managing organizational change and looking to implement AI-driven transformation effectively.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Leadership in AI Initiatives: ", "key_points_detail": "Gain the skills to lead AI projects, ensuring alignment with business goals and successful project execution from start to finish."}, {"key_points": "Strategic AI Integration: ", "key_points_detail": "Learn how to seamlessly integrate AI solutions into existing systems, driving innovation and improving operational efficiency across departments."}, {"key_points": "Optimized Program Management: ", "key_points_detail": "Develop expertise in managing resources, timelines, and cross-functional teams to deliver AI projects on time and within budget."}, {"key_points": "Enhanced Decision-Making: ", "key_points_detail": "Equip yourself with the ability to make data-driven, AI-informed decisions that drive business growth and competitive advantage."}, {"key_points": "Future-Proof Your Career: ", "key_points_detail": "Prepare for leadership roles in AI by mastering program management skills that are critical for navigating the rapidly evolving AI landscape."}]}, "lms_course_id": "822", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AIC_AI-Program-Director-Practitioner.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/AIC_AI-Program-Director-Practitioner.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:44:32.193238+02	2026-01-23 07:44:24.032765+02	2026-04-27 10:44:32.195379+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAIC_AI-Program-Director-Practitioner.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAIC_AI-Program-Director-Practitioner.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "Microsoft Project", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Microsoft-Outlook.png"}, {"name": "JIRA", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/jira.png"}, {"name": "Trello", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Frame-887-7-1.jpg"}, {"name": "Asana", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Asana.png"}, {"name": "Monday.com", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/monday.com_.png"}, {"name": "Basecamp", "