AI in Research</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: AI for Research Design and  Methodology", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Innovating Research Design with AI</li>\\n<li>6.2 AI in Survey Design and Implementation</li>\\n<li>6.3 Operational Efficiency and AI</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Ethical and Responsible Use of AI  in Research", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Ethical Considerations in AI Research</li>\\n<li>7.2 Data Privacy and AI</li>\\n<li>7.3 Developing and Implementing Ethical AI Guidelines</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Future of AI in Research", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Emerging Trends in AI Research</li>\\n<li>8.2 Preparing for the AI-Driven Research Future</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Researcher", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. What Are AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Key Capabilities of AI Agents in Research</li>\\n<li>3. Applications and Trends for AI Agents in Research</li>\\n<li>4. Benefits of AI Agents in Research</li>\\n<li>5. How Does an AI Agent Work</li>\\n<li>6. Core Characteristics of AI Agents</li>\\n<li>7. Types of AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Researcher.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Scholars &amp; Researchers</strong>: Enhance your research capabilities by integrating AI tools for data analysis and insight generation</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Market Research Analysts</strong><strong>: </strong>Leverage AI to optimize market research strategies, extract meaningful insights, and improve decision-making.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Data Scientists</strong><strong>: </strong>Apply AI methodologies to large d