an data-contrast=\\"auto\\"> Self-Paced: 8 hours of content</span></li>\\n</ul>\\n"}, "certification_modules": [{"certification_module_title": "Course Overview", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>Course Introduction <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O4sS_Vxc80w\\">Preview </a></li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 1: Introduction to Artificial Intelligence (AI) in Project Management", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>1.1 AI Fundamentals <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0tdUhCV7D5o\\">Preview </a></li>\\n<li>1.2 AI in Project Management<a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7U1r3TKeGM\\">Preview </a></li>\\n<li>1.3 Key AI Technologies</li>\\n<li>1.4 Benefits and Challenges</li>\\n<li>1.5 Future Perspectives</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: AI Tools for Project Management ", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>2.1 Overview of AI Tools <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xNh3Qf41mrY\\">Preview </a></li>\\n<li>2.2 Artificial Intelligence Tools in Action: Enhancing Project Management Efficiency <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z5oiJuDq_ts\\">Preview </a></li>\\n<li>2.3 Selecting AI Tools <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OCjBPVWJNic\\">Preview </a></li>\\n<li>2.4 Implementing AI Tools</li>\\n<li>2.5 Case Studies</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: Data-Driven Decision Making", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>3.1 Importance of Data in Artificial Intelligence <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pXSUrlx849Q\\">Preview </a></li>\\n<li>3.2 Data Analysis Techniques <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zu16bjGuqk4\\">Preview </a></li>\\n<li>3.3 Applying Data Insights to Project Decisions</li>\\n<li>3.4 Tools for Data Visualization and Reporting</li>\\n<li>3.5 Challenges and Best Practices</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: AI for Enhancing Team Collaboration and Productivity", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 AI-Enhanced Collaboration Tools</li>\\n<li>4.2 Boosting Productivity with AI</li>\\n<li>4.3 Managing Project Knowledge with AI</li>\\n<li>4.4 Overcoming Collaboration Challenges</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Ethical Considerations and Bias in AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Understanding AI Ethics</li>\\n<li>5.2 Identifying and Mitigating Bias</li>\\n<li>5.3 Developing AI Governance</li>\\n<li>5.4 Case Studies</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Implementing AI in Projects", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Strategies for AI Integration</li>\\n<li>6.2 Choosing the Right AI Tools</li>\\n<li>6.3 Project Data Preparation for AI</li>\\n<li>6.4 AI Implementation Plan</li>\\n<li>6.5 Monitoring AI Integration</li>\\n<li>6.6 Evaluating AI Outcomes</li>\\n<li>6.7 Risk Management in AI Projects</li>\\n<li>6.8 Workshop: AI Tool Deployment</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Future of AI in Project Management", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Emerging Trends in AI and Project Management</li>\\n<li>7.2 AI and the Evolving Role of the Project Manager</li>\\n<li>7.3 Sustainability and AI in Projects</li>\\n<li>7.4 Adapting to Future AI Development</li>\\n<li>7.5 Predictive Analysis and Future Planning</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Project Management", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. Understanding AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Case Studies</li>\\n<li>3. Hands-On Practice with AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Project-Manager.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_