ore AI Agent Functionalities</li>\\n<li>9.3 Introduction to AI Tools for Patent Drafting and Management</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 10: Case Outcome Prediction Agents", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>10.1 Introduction to Case Outcome Prediction?</li>\\n<li>10.2 Feature Engineering in Legal Case Outcome Prediction</li>\\n<li>10.3 The Rise of Multi-Agent Legal Workflows</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 11: Ethics, Fairness, and Transparency in Legal AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>11.1 Managing Bias in Legal AI</li>\\n<li>11.2 Legal Accountability in Autonomous Agent Deployment</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 12: Capstone Project – Building Your AI Legal Agent", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>12.1 Applying AI to Solve Real Legal Problems</li>\\n<li>12.2 Document Your Inputs and Prompts</li>\\n</ol>\\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FAIC_AI-Legal-Agent.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Legal Professionals:</strong> Lawyers, paralegals, and legal assistants seeking to enhance their work with AI-powered tools and automation.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Tech Enthusiasts:</strong> Individuals interested in exploring the intersection of AI and the legal industry to drive innovation.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Law Students:</strong> Students looking to stay ahead by gaining AI skills relevant to the evolving legal field.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Legal Operations Managers:</strong> Professionals aiming to streamline legal workflows and improve efficiency through AI-driven solutions.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "AI for Legal Professionals:", "key_points_detail": "Learn how AI enhances efficie