iding Examples</li>\\n<li>2.5 Evaluating Response Quality</li>\\n<li>2.6 Dividing Labor</li>\\n<li>2.7 Applying The Five Principles</li>\\n<li>2.8 Fixing Failing Prompts</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: Introduction to AI Tools and Models", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>3.1 Understanding AI Tools and Models <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=to3ShdNHWZw\\">Preview</a></li>\\n<li>3.2 Deep Dive into ChatGPT <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kpkrml2MKMY\\">Preview</a></li>\\n<li>3.3 Exploring GPT-4 <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7KdhSdzVWxY\\">Preview</a></li>\\n<li>3.4 Revolutionizing Art with DALL-E 2</li>\\n<li>3.5 Introduction to Emerging Tools using GPT</li>\\n<li>3.6 Specialized AI Models</li>\\n<li>3.7 Advanced AI Models</li>\\n<li>3.8 Google AI Innovations</li>\\n<li>3.9 Comparative Analysis of AI Tools</li>\\n<li>3.10 Practical Application Scenarios</li>\\n<li>3.11 Harnessing AI&#8217;s Potential</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: Mastering Prompt Engineering Techniques", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>4.1 Zero-Shot Prompting</li>\\n<li>4.2 Few-Shot Prompting</li>\\n<li>4.3 Chain-of-Thought Prompting</li>\\n<li>4.4 Ensuring Self-Consistency in AI Responses</li>\\n<li>4.5 Generate Knowledge Prompting</li>\\n<li>4.6 Prompt Chaining</li>\\n<li>4.7 Tree of Thoughts: Exploring Multiple Solutions</li>\\n<li>4.8 Retrieval Augmented Generation</li>\\n<li>4.9 Graph Prompting and Advanced Data Interpretation</li>\\n<li>4.10 Application in Practice: Real-Life Scenarios</li>\\n<li>4.11 Practical Exercises</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Mastering Image Model Techniques", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>5.1 Introduction to Image Models</li>\\n<li>5.2 Understanding Image Generation</li>\\n<li>5.3 Style Modifiers and Quality Boosters in Image Generation</li>\\n<li>5.4 Advanced Prompt Engineering in AI Image Generation</li>\\n<li>5.5 Prompt Rewriting for Image Models</li>\\n<li>5.6 Image Modification Techniques: Inpainting and Outpainting</li>\\n<li>5.7 Realistic Image Generation</li>\\n<li>5.8 Realistic Models and Consistent Characters</li>\\n<li>5.9 Practical Application of Image Model Techniques</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Project-Based Learning Session", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>6.1 Introduction to Project-Based Learning in AI</li>\\n<li>6.2 Selecting a Project Theme</li>\\n<li>6.3 Project Planning and Design in AI</li>\\n<li>6.4 AI Implementation and Prompt Engineering</li>\\n<li>6.5 Integrating Text and Image Models</li>\\n<li>6.6 Evaluation and Integration in AI Projects</li>\\n<li>6.7 Engaging and Effective Project Presentation</li>\\n<li>6.8 Guided Project Example</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Ethical Considerations and Future of AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>7.1 Introduction to AI Ethics</li>\\n<li>7.2 Bias and Fairness in AI Models</li>\\n<li>7.3 Privacy and Data Security in AI</li>\\n<li>7.4 The Imperative for Transparency in AI Operations</li>\\n<li>7.5 Sustainable AI Development: An Imperative for the Future</li>\\n<li>7.6 Ethical Scenario Analysis in AI: Navigating the Complex Landscape</li>\\n<li>7.7 Navigating the Complex Landscape of AI Regulations and Governance</li>\\n<li>7.8 Navigating the Regulatory Landscape: A Guide for AI Practitioners</li>\\n<li>7.9 Ethical Frameworks and Guidelines in AI Development</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Prompt Engineering", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. What Are AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Applications and Trends of AI Agents for Prompt Engineers</li>\\n<li>3. How Does an AI Agent Work</li>\\n<li>4. Core Characteristics of AI Agents</li>\\n<li>5. Importance of AI Agents</li>\\n<li>6. Types of AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Prompting-Fundamentals.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Research Scientists</strong>: Advance your research with AI by creating and utilizing effective prompts to explore new scientific data and solve complex problems.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Data Scientists &amp; Analysts:</strong> Enhance your ability to optimize machine learning models by mastering prompt engineering for better data analysis and insights.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Developers &amp; Programmers</strong><strong>:</strong> Learn to build, refine, and deploy AI-driven applications by creating efficient prompts for improved AI system performance.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Business Leaders &amp; Strategists</strong><strong>:</strong> Gain the skills to incorporate AI solutions into business strategies, optimizing processes and decision-making.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Machine Learning Engineers</strong><strong>:</strong> Strengthen your expertise by learning how to fine-tune AI prompts to enhance the performance of machine learning models.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Comprehensive AI Knowledge:", "key_points_detail": " Understand AI fundamentals, including machine learning, deep learning, and natural language processing. "}, {"key_points": "Advanced Prompt Engineering:", "key_points_detail": "Master key principles and advanced techniques to craft effective prompts and troubleshoot issues."}, {"key_points": "Practical AI Tools and Models:", "key_points_detail": "Gain hands-on experience with cutting-edge AI tools, text, and image generation models like GPT-4 and DALL-E 2."}, {"key_points": "Ethical AI Practices:", "key_points_detail": "Learn about AI ethics, including data security, privacy, and regulatory compliance to ensure responsible AI use. "}]}, "lms_course_id": "514", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Prompting-Fundamentals.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Prompting-Fundamentals.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:45:52.709351+02	2026-01-23 07:45:18.160844+02	2026-04-27 10:45:52.710876+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Prompting-Fundamentals.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Prompting-Fundamentals.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "LangChain", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/langchain-2.png"}, {"name": "OpenAI's GPT-4", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img-2.png"}]	\N	professional
