owth-Oriented:</b> Drive ethical business growth and maximize performance</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p><span data-ccp-props=\\"{}\\"> </span></p>\\n", "lms_course_id": "581", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Sales.svg", "trainer_prep_course_id": "", "certificate_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Sales.svg&output=jpg"}, "detail_data": {"id": 1069, "title": "AI+ Sales™", "ai_tools": [{"name": "Salesforce Einstein", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-9.jpg"}, {"name": "Conversica", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-30.png"}, {"name": "Uniphore", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img.png"}], "description": "<ul>\\n<li><b>Sales Transformation:</b> Harness AI to boost sales operations, CRM integration, and forecasting</li>\\n</ul>\\n<ul>\\n<li><b>Hands-on Approach:</b> Practical workshops covering AI tools and ethical sales practices</li>\\n</ul>\\n<ul>\\n<li><b>Data-Driven Insights:</b> Learn to analyze, optimize, and automate sales processes</li>\\n</ul>\\n<ul>\\n<li><b>Growth-Oriented:</b> Drive ethical business growth and maximize performance</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p><span data-ccp-props=\\"{}\\"> </span></p>\\n", "lms_course_id": "581", "course_tagline": "Boost Sales Success Through AI-Driven Insights", "certificate_code": "AP-270", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Sales.svg", "certificate_overview": {"exam_format": "50 questions, 70% passing, 90 minutes, online proctored exam ", "prerequisites": "Basic familiarity with sales processes, proficiency in data analysis, Primary knowledge of CRM systems ", "included_items": "Instructor-led OR Self-paced course + Official exam + Digital badge ", "certificate_duration": "<ul>\\n<li>Instructor-Led: 1 day (live or virtual)</li>\\n<li>Self-Paced: 8 hours of content</li>\\n</ul>\\n"}, "certification_modules": [{"certification_module_title": "Course Overview", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>Course Introduction <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hjEkM11mY5w\\">Preview</a></li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 1: Introduction to Artificial Intelligence (AI) in Sales", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1.1 Fundamentals of AI</li>\\n<li>1.2 Historical Journey and Evolution of AI in Sales</li>\\n<li>1.3 AI Tools &amp; Technologies Transforming Sales</li>\\n<li>1.4 Benefits and Challenges in Adoption of AI in Sales</li>\\n<li>1.5 Real-world Examples and Applications of AI in Sales</li>\\n<li>1.6 Future of AI in Sales</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: Understanding Data in Sales", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>2.1 Categories of Sales Data</li>\\n<li>2.2 Techniques for Effective Data Collection</li>\\n<li>2.3 Basics of Data Analysis and Interpretation</li>\\n<li>2.4 Data Management Methods</li>\\n<li>2.5 Data Protection Principles</li>\\n<li>2.6 Data Integration in CRM Systems</li>\\n<li>2.7 Overview of Analytical Tools</li>\\n<li>2.8 Ethical Use of Sales Data</li>\\n<li>2.9 Case Studies: Real-World Data Applications</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: AI Technologies for Sales ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>3.1 Introduction to Machine Learning in Sales</li>\\n<li>3.2 Predictive Analytics: Forecasting Sales Trends</li>\\n<li>3.3 NLP: Enhancing Customer Interactions</li>\\n<li>3.4 Chatbots: Automating Customer Service</li>\\n<li>3.5 Segmentation: Tailoring Customer Experiences</li>\\n<li>3.6 Personalization: Customizing Sales Approaches</li>\\n<li>3.7 Recommendation Engines: Driving Product Suggestions</li>\\n<li>3.8 Sales Automation: Streamlining Sales Processes</li>\\n<li>3.9 Performance Analysis: Measuring Sales Effectiveness</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: Implementation of AI in CRM Systems ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 Foundation of CRM Systems</li>\\n<li>4.2 AI Integration into CRM Systems</li>\\n<li>4.3 Lead Scoring</li>\\n<li>4.4 Customer Insights</li>\\n<li>4.5 Sales Automation</li>\\n<li>4.6 Personalized Communication</li>\\n<li>4.7 Chatbots in CRM</li>\\n<li>4.8 Gaining Actionable Insights from Data</li>\\n<li>4.9 Case Studies</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Sales Forecasting with AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Introduction to Sales Forecasting</li>\\n<li>5.2 Overview of Predictive Models in Forecasting</li>\\n<li>5.3 Data Preparation for Analysis</li>\\n<li>5.4 Identifying Sales Patterns and Trends</li>\\n<li>5.5 Enhancing Forecast Reliability</li>\\n<li>5.6 Key Forecasting AI Tools in AI</li>\\n<li>5.7 Utilizing Real-time Data for Forecasts</li>\\n<li>5.8 Developing Forecasts for Different Outcomes</li>\\n<li>5.9 Measuring the Success of Sales Forecasts</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Enhancing Sales Processes with AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Task Automation</li>\\n<li>6.2 AI-driven Email Marketing</li>\\n<li>6.3 Social Media with AI Analytics</li>\\n<li>6.4 AI-powered Lead Generation</li>\\n<li>6.5 Customer Segmentation</li>\\n<li>6.6 Optimizing Sales Visits and Calls</li>\\n<li>6.7 Tailoring Content with AI Insights</li>\\n<li>6.8 Real-time Sales Activity Monitoring</li>\\n<li>6.9 Upselling and Cross-selling with AI</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Ethical Considerations and Bias AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Ethical Use of AI in Sales</li>\\n<li>7.2 Bias Identification in AI Systems</li>\\n<li>7.3 Bias Mitigation</li>\\n<li>7.4 Transparency in AI Decision-Making</li>\\n<li>7.5 Accountability for AI Actions</li>\\n<li>7.6 Safeguarding Customer Data</li>\\n<li>7.7 Regulatory Compliance</li>\\n<li>7.8 Building Customer Trust through Ethical AI</li>\\n<li>7.9 Anticipating Ethical Issues in AI Advancements</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Practical Workshop", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Scenario-Based Exercises</li>\\n<li>8.2 Addressing Sales Challenges with AI</li>\\n<li>8.3 Collaborative AI Implementation Plans</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module:  AI Agents for Sales", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. What Are AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Types of AI Agents</li>\\n<li>3. Applications and Trend of AI Agents in Sales</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Sales.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Sales Executives</strong>: Use AI to automate sales processes and enhance customer relationship management for improved sales performance.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Marketing Professionals</strong><strong>:</strong> Integrate AI with marketing strategies to customer targeting, personalization, and engagement.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Business Development Managers</strong><strong>:</strong> Leverage AI-driven insights to identify new business opportunities and drive growth.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Product Managers</strong><strong>:</strong> Utilize AI to understand customer needs, optimize pricing strategies, and improve product positioning.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Consultants:</strong> Help organizations implement AI-powered sales strategies that drive profitability and operational efficiency.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Comprehensive AI Understanding:", "key_points_detail": "Learn core AI concepts for streamlined sales workflows, trend forecasting, and client engagement. "}, {"key_points": "Predictive Sales Analytics:", "key_points_detail": "Learn to leverage AI for predictive modeling, forecasting sales, and enhancing decision-making. "}, {"key_points": "AI-Enhanced Customer Insights:", "key_points_detail": "Explore AI tools to analyze behavior, automate scoring, and personalize outreach effectively. "}, {"key_points": "Ethical AI Integration:", "key_points_detail": "Gain insights on addressing ethical concerns and establishing AI governance in sales. \\r\\n"}]}, "lms_course_id": "581", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Sales.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Sales.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:46:06.589895+02	2026-01-23 07:45:27.591602+02	2026-04-27 10:46:06.591216+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Sales.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Sales.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "Salesforce Einstein", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-9.jpg"}, {"name": "Conversica", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-30.png"}, {"name": "Uniphore", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img.png"}]	\N	professional
