siness management or technical tools, such as ERP systems or data analysis software, will be beneficial. ", "included_items": "Instructor-led OR Self-paced course + Official exam + Digital badge", "certificate_duration": "<ul>\\n<li>Instructor-Led: 1 day (live or virtual)</li>\\n<li> Self-Paced: 8 hours of content</li>\\n</ul>\\n"}, "certification_modules": [{"certification_module_title": "Module 1: Introduction to Artificial Intelligence in Supply Chain", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1.1 Overview of Artificial Intelligence in Supply Chain Management (SCM)</li>\\n<li>1.2 Transforming Supply Chains with AI</li>\\n<li>1.3 Ethical Implications of AI in Supply Chains</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: Advanced AI Techniques for Supply Chain", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>2.1 Machine Learning in Supply Chain</li>\\n<li>2.2 Expert Systems in SCM</li>\\n<li>2.3 Integrating Images and Text in Supply Chain AI</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: Generative AI in Supply Chain Management", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>3.1 The Origin of Generative AI</li>\\n<li>3.2 Generative AI in Revenue Management and Demand Forecasting</li>\\n<li>3.3 Transformer and LSTM Architectures in Generative AI</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: Supply Chain Digitization", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 Introduction to Supply Chain Digitization</li>\\n<li>4.2 Supply Chain Integration and Push-Pull Strategies</li>\\n<li>4.3 Supply Chain Resiliency, Planning and Sustainability</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Intelligent Driven Supply Chain Management", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Introduction to Smart SCM</li>\\n<li>5.2 Employing Smart SCM and Prompt Engineering</li>\\n<li>5.3 Future Trends of Smart SCM</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Industry Aspects of Advanced SCM", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Introduction to Industrial SCM</li>\\n<li>6.2 Business Value from AI and Gen AI in Supply Chain</li>\\n<li>6.3 Risks and Challenges of Adopting AI and Gen AI in Industrial SCM</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Policies of Logistics Management in Supply Chain with AI", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Role of Supply Chain Management in the Organization</li>\\n<li>7.2 Warehousing Strategy for Efficient Supply Chain Management</li>\\n<li>7.3 Technical Coverage of SCM with Multi-Dimensional Aspects</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Supply Chain Masterclass with AI Assistance", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Supplier Selection and Relationship Management with AI</li>\\n<li>8.2 Mastering Advancements in SCM with Modern Artefacts</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Supply Chain", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>What Are AI Agents</li>\\n<li>What Are AI Agents in Logistics and Supply Chain</li>\\n<li> Applications &amp; Trends of AI Agents in Supply Chain</li>\\n<li>How Does an AI Agent Work</li>\\n<li>Core Characteristics of AI Agents</li>\\n<li>Key Advantages of AI Agents in Logistics and Supply Chain</li>\\n<li>Types of AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAIC_AI-Supply-Chain-1.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Supply Chain Professionals</strong>: Enhance your supply chain management skills by integrating AI tools for improved forecasting, inventory management, and process optimization.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Logistics &amp; Operations Managers</strong>: Learn to leverage AI for optimizing logistics, route planning, and warehouse management to enhance operational efficiency and reduce costs.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Procurement Experts</strong>: Use AI to improve supplier selection, demand forecasting, and inventory replenishment, streamlining procurement processes.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Business Leaders</strong>: Drive innovation in your supply chain by adopting AI technologies to automate workflows, predict demand, and optimize end-to-end operations.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Students &amp; New Graduates</strong>: Gain a competitive advantage in the supply chain field by mastering AI tools and techniques that are transforming global logistics and supply chain management.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Leverage AI for Smarter Supply Chain Operations:", "key_points_detail": "Learn how AI tools can optimize logistics, reduce costs, and improve supply chain efficiency from end to end."}, {"key_points": "Optimize Demand Forecasting with AI:", "key_points_detail": "Use AI-driven analytics to predict demand, streamline inventory management, and reduce stockouts or overstocking."}, {"key_points": "Stay Ahead in AI-Powered Supply Chain:", "key_points_detail": "As industries increasingly adopt AI, professionals with AI supply chain expertise are in high demand to drive innovation and efficiency."}, {"key_points": "Enhance Decision-Making with Predictive Analytics:", "key_points_detail": "Master AI algorithms to analyze supply chain data and make informed, real-time decisions to improve overall operations."}]}, "lms_course_id": "505", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/AIC_AI-Supply-Chain-1.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/AIC_AI-Supply-Chain-1.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:45:29.257874+02	2026-01-23 07:45:01.723266+02	2026-04-27 10:45:29.25951+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAIC_AI-Supply-Chain-1.svg&output=jpg	https: