li>4.1 Introduction to Neural Networks in Image Processing</li>\\n<li>4.2 Neural Networks for Sequential Data</li>\\n<li>4.3 Practical Implementation of Neural Networks</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Significance of Large Language Models (LLM)", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Exploring Large Language Models</li>\\n<li>5.2 Popular Large Language Models</li>\\n<li>5.3 Practical Finetuning of Language Models</li>\\n<li>5.4 Hands-on: Practical Finetuning for Text Classification</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Application of Generative AI ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Introduction to Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs)</li>\\n<li>6.2 Applications of Variational Autoencoders (VAEs)</li>\\n<li>6.3 Generating Realistic Data Using Generative Models</li>\\n<li>6.4 Hands-on: Implementing Generative Models for Image Synthesis</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Natural Language Processing ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 NLP in Real-world Scenarios</li>\\n<li>7.2 Attention Mechanisms and Practical Use of Transformers</li>\\n<li>7.3 In-depth Understanding of BERT for Practical NLP Tasks</li>\\n<li>7.4 Hands-on: Building Practical NLP Pipelines with Pretrained Models</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Transfer Learning with Hugging Face ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Overview of Transfer Learning in AI</li>\\n<li>8.2 Transfer Learning Strategies and Techniques</li>\\n<li>8.3 Hands-on: Implementing Transfer Learning with Hugging Face Models for Various Tasks</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 9: Crafting Sophisticated GUIs for AI Solutions ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>9.1 Overview of GUI-based AI Applications</li>\\n<li>9.2 Web-based Framework</li>\\n<li>9.3 Desktop Application Framework</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 10: AI Communication and Deployment Pipeline ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>10.1 Communicating AI Results Effectively to Non-Technical Stakeholders</li>\\n<li>10.2 Building a Deployment Pipeline for AI Models</li>\\n<li>10.3 Developing Prototypes Based on Client Requirements</li>\\n<li>10.4 Hands-on: Deployment</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Engineering", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. Understanding AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Case Studies</li>\\n<li>3. Hands-On Practice with AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Engineer.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>AI &amp; Software Engineers:</strong> Enhance your development skills by mastering AI techniques and designing advanced AI systems.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Machine Learning Enthusiasts:</strong> Apply deep learning, neural networks, and NLP techniques to real-world AI challenges.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Data Scientists: </strong>Strengthen your AI toolkit with engineering techniques for building and deploying scalable AI solutions.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>IT Specialists &amp; System Architects:</strong> Integrate AI solutions into existing infrastructures, optimizing performance and scalability.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Students &amp; New Graduates:</strong> Develop in-demand AI engineering skills and prepare for a successful career in the rapidly growing AI field.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Master AI System Design:", "key_points_detail": "Develop the skills to design, implement, and optimize advanced AI systems for real-world applications. "}, {"key_points": "Build Scalable AI Solutions:", "key_points_detail": "Learn how to create scalable AI solutions for industries like technology, finance, and healthcare. "}, {"key_points": "Tackle Complex Engineering Challenges:", "key_points_detail": "This certification ensures you’re equipped to solve challenges in AI architecture, neural networks, and NLP. "}, {"key_points": "Contribute to AI-Driven Innovations:", "key_points_detail": "Certified AI+ Engineers develop cutting-edge AI solutions that enhance business operations and drive future innovations. "}, {"key_points": "Advance Your Career in AI Engineering:", "key_points_detail": " As demand for skilled AI engineers rises, this certification offers a competitive advantage in the job market. "}]}, "lms_course_id": "600", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Engineer.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Engineer.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:45:56.537237+02	2026-01-23 07:45:20.857791+02	2026-04-27 10:45:56.539285+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Engineer.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Engineer.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "TensorFlow", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-38.jpg"}, {"name": "Hugging Face Transformers", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-1-2.jpg"}, {"name": "Jenkins", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image.png"}, {"name": "TensorFlow Hub", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-7-7.jpg"}]	\N	technical
