ng Reliable Quantum Strategies with AI:", "key_points_detail": "Certified professionals play a key role in developing quantum strategies that ensure performance, reliability, and alignment with industry standards. "}, {"key_points": "Gaining a Competitive Edge:", "key_points_detail": "As quantum computing and AI continue to revolutionize industries, this certification provides professionals with a competitive edge, preparing them for advanced roles. "}]}, "lms_course_id": "639", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Quantum.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Quantum.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:46:33.751444+02	2026-01-23 07:45:48.178593+02	2026-04-27 10:46:33.753097+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Quantum.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Quantum.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "IBM Qiskit", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-4-2.png"}, {"name": "D-Wave Leap", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Frame-887.jpg"}, {"name": "Google TensorFlow Quantum (TFQ)", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Frame-887-22.jpg"}, {"name": "Amazon Braket", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Frame-886-8.jpg"}]	\N	technical
