>\\n<li class=\\"pf0\\"><span class=\\"cf0\\"><strong>Core Concepts Covered:</strong> </span><span class=\\"cf1\\">Learn AI fundamentals for finance, focusing on analytics, trading, risk, fraud, automation<br />\\n</span></li>\\n<li class=\\"pf0\\"><strong><span class=\\"cf0\\">Capstone Application: </span></strong><span class=\\"cf1\\">Build practical AI finance agents supporting trading, risk evaluation, fraud monitoring, and forecasting<br />\\n</span></li>\\n<li class=\\"pf0\\"><strong><span class=\\"cf0\\">Career Readiness: </span></strong><span class=\\"cf1\\">Gain expertise in AI-powered financial roles through mentorship, hands-on training, designing AI agents for finance innovation</span><!--EndFragment --></li>\\n</ul>\\n", "lms_course_id": "802", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/AIC_AI-Finance-Agent.svg", "trainer_prep_course_id": "", "certificate_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FAIC_AI-Finance-Agent.svg&output=jpg"}, "detail_data": {"id": 31192, "title": "AI+ Finance Agent™", "ai_tools": [{"name": "Python", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Python.png"}, {"name": "TensorFlow", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-38.jpg"}, {"name": "Pandas", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/pandas.png"}, {"name": "NumPy", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/NumPy.png"}, {"name": "Power BI", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Power-BI.png"}, {"name": "SQL", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/sql.png"}, {"name": "OpenAI API", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/OpenAI-AP.png"}, {"name": "APIs", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/RESTful-APIs.png"}], "description": "<p><!--StartFragment --></p>\\n<ul>\\n<li class=\\"pf0\\"><span class=\\"cf0\\"><strong>Core Concepts Covered:</strong> </span><span class=\\"cf1\\">Learn AI fundamentals for finance, focusing on analytics, trading, risk, fraud, automation<br />\\n</span></li>\\n<li class=\\"pf0\\"><strong><span class=\\"cf0\\">Capstone Application: </span></strong><span class=\\"cf1\\">Build practical AI finance agents supporting trading, risk evaluation, fraud monitoring, and forecasting<br />\\n</span></li>\\n<li class=\\"pf0\\"><strong><span class=\\"cf0\\">Career Readiness: </span></strong><span class=\\"cf1\\">Gain expertise in AI-powered financial roles through mentorship, hands-on training, designing AI agents for finance innovation</span><!--EndFragment --></li>\\n</ul>\\n", "lms_course_id": "802", "course_tagline": "Empower organizations with AI+ Finance Agent™ to automate financial operations and improve decisions", "certificate_code": "AP 2201", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/AIC_AI-Finance-Agent.svg", "certificate_overview": {"exam_format": "50 questions, 70% passing, 90 minutes, online proctored exam", "prerequisites": "Basic Knowledge of Financial Markets, Familiarity with Machine Learning, Programming Skills, Statistical Analysis Understanding, Interest in Financial Technology", "included_items": "Instructor-led OR Self-paced course + Official exam + Digital badge", "certificate_duration": "<ul>\\n<li>Instructor-Led: 1 day (live or virtual)</li>\\n<li>Self-Paced: 8 hours of content</li>\\n</ul>\\n"}, "certification_modules": [{"certification_module_title": "Module 1: Introduction to AI Agents in Finance", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1.1 Understanding AI Agents in Finance vs Traditional Financial Automation</li>\\n<li>1.2 The Evolution of AI Agents in Financial Services</li>\\n<li>1.3 Overview of Different Types of AI Agents in Finance</li>\\n<li>1.4 Importance of Agent Autonomy and Task Delegation in Financial Settings</li>\\n<li>1.5 Key Differences Between AI Agents in Finance and Traditional Automation</li>\\n<li>1.6 Hands-On Activity: Exploring AI Agents in Finance</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: Building and Understanding AI Agents in Finance", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>2.1 Architecture of AI Agents in Finance</li>\\n<li>2.2 Tools and Libraries for Agent Development</li>\\n<li>2.3 AI Agents vs. Static Models</li>\\n<li>2.4 Overview of Agent Lifecycle</li>\\n<li>2.5 Use Case: Customer Support Agents in Banks for Handling KYC, FAQs, and Transaction Disputes</li>\\n<li>2.6 Case Study: Bank of America’s Erica: A Virtual Financial Assistant that Handles 1+ Billion Interactions Using Predictive AI</li>\\n<li>2.7 Hands-On Activity: Building and Understanding AI Agents in Finance</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: Intelligent Agents for Fraud Detection and Anomaly Monitoring", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>3.1 Supervised/Unsupervised ML for Fraud Detection</li>\\n<li>3.2 Pattern Analysis &amp; Behavioural Profiling</li>\\n<li>3.3 Real-time Monitoring Agents</li>\\n<li>3.4 Real-World Use Case: AI Agents Monitoring Transaction Behaviour and Flagging Anomalies for Real-Time Fraud Detection in Digital Wallets</li>\\n<li>3.5 Case Study: PayPal&#8217;s AI System Uses Graph-Based Anomaly Detection Agents to Flag 0.32% of All Transactions for Fraud with 99.9% Accuracy</li>\\n<li>3.6 Hands-On Activity: Intelligent Agents for Fraud Detection and Anomaly Monitoring</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: AI Agents for Credit Scoring and Lending Automation", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 Feature Generation from Non-Traditional Credit Data</li>\\n<li>4.2 Explainability (XAI) in Credit Decisions</li>\\n<li>4.3 Bias Mitigation in Lending Agents</li>\\n<li>4.4 Real-World Use Case: Agents Assessing New-to-Credit Individuals Using Transaction and Mobile Data</li>\\n<li>4.5 Case Study: Upstart’s AI-Based Lending Platform Approved by CFPB Showed 27% Increase in Approval Rate and 16% Lower APRs for Borrowers</li>\\n<li>4.6 Hands-On Activity: AI Agents for Credit Scoring and Lending Automation</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: AI Agents for Wealth Management and Robo-Advisory", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Personalization Using Profiling Agents</li>\\n<li>5.2 Portfolio Rebalancing Algorithms</li>\\n<li>5.3 Sentiment-Aware Investing</li>\\n<li>5.4 Real-World Use Case: AI Agent Adjusting Portfolio Weekly Based on Financial Goals and Market Trends</li>\\n<li>5.5 Case Study: Wealthfront’s Path Agent Uses Financial Behavior Modeling to Recommend Personalized Savings Goals and Investment Paths</li>\\n<li>5.6 Hands-On Activity: AI Agents for Wealth Management and Robo-Advisory</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Trading Bots and Market-Monitoring Agents", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Reinforcement Learning in Trading Agents</li>\\n<li>6.2 Predictive Modelling Using Historical Data</li>\\n<li>6.3 Risk-Reward Threshold Management</li>\\n<li>6.4 Real-World Use Case: AI Trading Agents Performing Arbitrage Between Crypto Exchanges</li>\\n<li>6.4 Case Study: Renaissance Technologies Utilizes AI to Automate Short-Hold Trades, Generating Consistent Alpha via Adaptive Trading Bots</li>\\n<li>6.5 Hands-On Activity: Trading Bots and Market-Monitoring Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: NLP Agents for Financial Document Intelligence", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 LLMs in Earnings Call and Filings Analysis</li>\\n<li>7.2 AI Summarization and Event Detection</li>\\n<li>7.3 Voice-to-Text and Key-Point Extraction</li>\\n<li>7.4 Real-World Use Case</li>\\n<li>7.5 Case Study: BloombergGPT — A Financial-Grade Large Language Model</li>\\n<li>7.6 Hands-On Activity: NLP Agents for Financial Document Intelligence</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Compliance and Risk Surveillance Agents", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 AI for Anti-Money Laundering (AML) and Know Your Business (KYB)</li>\\n<li>8.2 Regulation-aware Rule Modelling</li>\\n<li>8.3 Transaction Graph Analysis</li>\\n<li>8.4 Real-World Use Case: Agent tracking suspicious cross-border money transfers in real-time across multiple accounts.</li>\\n<li>8.5 Case Study: HSBC uses Quantexa’s AI agents to trace AML networks, increasing suspicious activity detection by 30%.</li>\\n<li>8.6 Hands-On Activity: Compliance and Risk Surveillance Agents in Financial Systems</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 9: Responsible, Fair & Auditable AI Agents", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>9.1 Governance Frameworks for AI in Finance (RBI, EU AI Act)</li>\\n<li>9.2 Transparency and Auditability in Decision Logic</li>\\n<li>9.3 Fairness and Explainability</li>\\n<li>9.4 Real-World Use Case: Auditable AI Agent Logs Used During Internal Policy Audits to Ensure Fair Lending practices.</li>\\n<li>9.5 Case Study: Wells Fargo implemented internal AI fairness reviews for lending bots post regulatory scrutiny.</li>\\n<li>9.6 Hands-On Activity: Responsible, Fair &amp; Auditable AI Agents in Finance</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 10: World Famous Case Studies", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>10.1 Case Study 1: JPMorgan’s COiN Platform</li>\\n<li>10.2 Case Study 2: AI in Fraud Detection &#8211; PayPal’s Decision Intelligence</li>\\n<li>10.3 Case Study: AI-Driven Credit Scoring &#8211; Upstart’s Lending Platform</li>\\n<li>10.4 Capstone Project</li>\\n<li>10.5 Key Takeaways of the Module</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FAIC_AI-Finance-Agent.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Finance Professionals: </strong>Ideal for analysts, accountants, and financial managers looking to integrate AI into everyday workflows.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Investment &amp; Portfolio Specialists:</strong> Suited for individuals aiming to enhance forecasting, risk modeling, and data-driven investment strategies.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Fintech Enthusiasts:</strong> Perfect for learners interested in the intersection of AI, automation, and modern financial technologies.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Data &amp; Tech Professionals:</strong> Great for those with analytical or programming backgrounds seeking to apply AI in financial domains.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Business Leaders &amp; Decision-Makers:</strong> Beneficial for executives wanting to leverage AI for smarter budgeting, planning, and strategic financial growth.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Financial Accuracy & Reliability: ", "key_points_detail": "AI automation reduces manual errors and enhances precision across reconciliation, reporting, and day-to-day finance tasks."}, {"key_points": "Strategic Insight & Intelligence: ", "key_points_detail": "Data-driven forecasting and analytics empower faster, smarter decisions in budgeting, planning, and financial strategy."}, {"key_points": "Risk Management & Compliance Strength:", "key_points_detail": "AI tools elevate fraud detection, regulatory oversight, and secure handling of sensitive financial data."}, {"key_points": "Operational Efficiency in Finance:", "key_points_detail": "Intelligent automation streamlines routine workflows, enabling teams to focus on high-impact financial initiatives."}, {"key_points": "Career Advancement in Digital Finance:", "key_points_detail": "Certification positions professionals at the forefront of AI-enabled finance transformation, increasing market relevance."}]}, "lms_course_id": "802", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/AIC_AI-Finance-Agent.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/AIC_AI-Finance-Agent.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:45:00.17705+02	2026-01-23 07:44:41.672639+02	2026-04-27 10:45:00.178667+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FAIC_AI-Finance-Agent.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FAIC_AI-Finance-Agent.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "Python", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Python.png"}, {"name": "TensorFlow", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-38.jpg"}, {"name": "Pandas", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/pandas.png"}, {"name": "NumPy", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/NumPy.png"}, {"name": "Power BI", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Power-BI.png"}, {"name": "SQL", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/sql.png"}, {"name": "OpenAI API", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/OpenAI-AP.png"}, {"name": "APIs", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/RESTful-APIs.png"}]	\N	professional
