n<li>7.1 Introduction to Generative AI Tools</li>\\n<li>7.2 Applications of Generative AI</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Machine Learning", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Introduction to Supervised Learning Algorithms</li>\\n<li>8.2 Introduction to Unsupervised Learning</li>\\n<li>8.3 Different Algorithms for Clustering</li>\\n<li>8.4 Association Rule Learning with Implementation</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 9: Advance Machine Learning", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>9.1 Ensemble Learning Techniques</li>\\n<li>9.2 Dimensionality Reduction</li>\\n<li>9.3 Advanced Optimization Techniques</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 10: Data-Driven Decision-Making", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>10.1 Introduction to Data-Driven Decision Making</li>\\n<li>10.2 Open Source Tools for Data-Driven Decision Making</li>\\n<li>10.3 Deriving Data-Driven Insights from Sales Dataset</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 11: Data Storytelling", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>11.1 Understanding the Power of Data Storytelling</li>\\n<li>11.2 Identifying Use Cases and Business Relevance</li>\\n<li>11.3 Crafting Compelling Narratives</li>\\n<li>11.4 Visualizing Data for Impact</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 12: Capstone Project - Employee Attrition Prediction", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>12.1 Project Introduction and Problem Statement</li>\\n<li>12.2 Data Collection and Preparation</li>\\n<li>12.3 Data Analysis and Modeling</li>\\n<li>12.4 Data Storytelling and Presentation</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Data Analysis", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. Understanding AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Case Studies</li>\\n<li>3. Hands-On Practice with AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.