_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 Contextual and Role-Based Prompting</li>\\n<li>4.2 Adaptive and Multimodal Prompting</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Integration with Development Tools", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Integrating with Popular Development Tools for Prompt<br />\\nEngineering</li>\\n<li>5.2 Code Repositories and Templates for Prompt<br />\\nEngineering</li>\\n<li>5.3 Developer Communities and Forums for Prompt<br />\\nEngineering</li>\\n<li>5.4 Version Control in Prompt Engineering Projects</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Applications of Prompt Engineering in Various Domains", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Natural Language Processing (NLP) Applications using<br />\\nPrompt Engineering</li>\\n<li>6.2 Business Applications using Prompt Engineering</li>\\n<li>6.3 Creative Applications using Prompt Engineering</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Project-Based Learning: Real-World AI Projects Using Prompt Engineering", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Project 1: AI-Driven Customer Support</li>\\n<li>7.2 Project 2: Personalized Content Generation</li>\\n<li>7.3 Project 3: AI in Data Analysis</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Prompt Engineering", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. What Are AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Applications and Trends of AI Agents for Prompt Engineers</li>\\n<li>3. Importance of AI Agents</li>\\n<li>4. Types of AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAIC_AI-Prompt-Engineer-Level-2.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>AI Developers:</strong> Enhance your prompt engineering skills and optimize AI-driven applications for diverse use cases.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><s