ational choices</span></li>\\n<li><span data-teams=\\"true\\"><strong>Comprehensive AI Understanding:</strong> Covers AI fundamentals to real-world healthcare applications</span></li>\\n<li><span data-teams=\\"true\\"><strong>Clinical Excellence with AI:</strong> Empowers nurses to confidently integrate AI into daily healthcare practice</span></li>\\n</ul>\\n", "lms_course_id": "730", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/AIC_AI-Nurse.svg", "trainer_prep_course_id": "", "certificate_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FAIC_AI-Nurse.svg&output=jpg"}, "detail_data": {"id": 31195, "title": "AI+ Nurse™", "ai_tools": [{"name": "Python", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Python.png"}, {"name": "Scikit-learn", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-53.jpg"}, {"name": "Keras", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Keras.png"}, {"name": "Jupyter Notebooks", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jupyter.jpg"}, {"name": "Matplotlib", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Matplotlib.png"}, {"name": "Power BI", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Power-BI.png"}], "description": "<ul>\\n<li><span data-teams=\\"true\\"><strong>Patient-Centric AI Care:</strong> Designed for nurses to leverage AI for enhanced patient outcomes</span></li>\\n<li><span data-teams=\\"true\\"><strong>Data-Driven Decisions:</strong> Provides practical insights for informed clinical and operational choices</span></li>\\n<li><span data-teams=\\"true\\"><strong>Comprehensive AI Understanding:</strong> Covers AI fundamentals to real-world healthcare applications</span></li>\\n<li><span data-teams=\\"true\\"><strong>Clinical Excellence with AI:</strong> Empowers nurses to confidently integrate AI into daily healthcare practice</span></li>\\n</ul>\\n", "lms_course_id": "730", "course_tagline": "Blending Human Touch with AI Intelligence", "certificate_code": "AP 1102", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/AIC_AI-Nurse.svg", "certificate_overview": {"exam_format": "50 questions, 70% passing, 90 minutes, online proctored exam", "prerequisites": "Basic nursing knowledge, Familiarity with healthcare technology, Critical thinking, Foundational AI and ML concepts, Problem solving skills", "included_items": "Instructor-led OR Self-paced course + Official exam + Digital badge", "certificate_duration": "<ul>\\n<li>Instructor-Led: 1 day (live or virtual)</li>\\n<li>Self-Paced: 8 hours of content</li>\\n</ul>\\n"}, "certification_modules": [{"certification_module_title": "Module 1: What is AI for Nurses?", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1.1 What is AI for Nurses?</li>\\n<li>1.2 Where AI Shows Up in Nursing</li>\\n<li>1.3 Case Study: Improving Patient Safety and Nursing Efficiency with AI at Riverside Medical Center</li>\\n<li>1.4 Hands-on: Using Nurse AI for Clinical Data Visualization in Postoperative Nursing Care</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: AI for Documentation, Workflow, and Data Literacy", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>2.1 Introduction to Natural Language Processing</li>\\n<li>2.2 Workflow Automation: Transforming Nursing Practice</li>\\n<li>2.3 Beginner’s Guide to Data Literacy in Nursing</li>\\n<li>2.4 Legal &amp; Compliance Basics in Nursing AI Documentation</li>\\n<li>2.5 Case Study: Integrating AI and Workflow Automation at Massachusetts General Hospital (MGH)</li>\\n<li>2.6 Hands-On Exercise: Using the ChatGPT Registered Nurse Tool in Clinical Documentation and Patient Education</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: Predictive AI and Patient Safety", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>3.1 Understanding Predictive Models</li>\\n<li>3.2 Alert Fatigue and Trust</li>\\n<li>3.3 Simulation Activity: Responding to Real-Time Deterioration Alerts</li>\\n<li>3.4 Collaborating Across Teams</li>\\n<li>3.5 Bias in Predictions</li>\\n<li>3.6 Case Study</li>\\n<li>3.7 Hands-on Activity: Interpreting Predictive Alerts with ChatGPT</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: Generative AI in Nursing", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 Introduction to Generative AI in Nursing</li>\\n<li>4.2 Large Language Models (LLMs) for Nurses</li>\\n<li>4.3 Creating Patient Education Materials with AI</li>\\n<li>4.4 Ensuring Safe and Ethical Use of AI</li>\\n<li>4.5 Case Study</li>\\n<li>4.6 Hands-On Activity: Exploring AI-Powered Differential Diagnosis with Symptoma</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Ethics, Safety, and Advocacy in AI Integration", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Bias, Fairness, and Inclusion</li>\\n<li>5.2 Informed Consent and Transparency</li>\\n<li>5.3 Nurse Advocacy and Professional Responsibilities</li>\\n<li>5.4 Creating an Ethics Checklist</li>\\n<li>5.5 Stakeholder Feedback Techniques</li>\\n<li>5.6 Legal and Regulatory Considerations</li>\\n<li>5.7 Psychological and Social Implications</li>\\n<li>5.8 Case Study: Addressing Racial Bias in Healthcare Algorithms (Optum Algorithm Case).</li>\\n<li>5.9 Hands-on: Uncovering Bias in Diabetes Risk Prediction: A Fairness Audit Using Aequitas</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Evaluating and Selecting AI Tools", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Understanding Performance Metrics</li>\\n<li>6.2 Vendor Red Flags</li>\\n<li>6.3 Nurse Role in Selection</li>\\n<li>6.4 Evaluation Templates and Checklists</li>\\n<li>6.5 Use Cases: AI in Clinical Decision-Making</li>\\n<li>6.6 Case Study: Using AI to Enhance Real-Time Clinical Decision-Making at UAB Medicine with MIC Sickbay</li>\\n<li>6.7 Hands-on: Evaluating AI Diagnostic Model Performance Using Confusion Matrix Metrics</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Implementing AI and Leading Change on the Unit", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Building Buy-In: Promoting AI as an Ally, Not a Competitor</li>\\n<li>7.2 Change Management Essentials</li>\\n<li>7.3 Creating an AI Playbook: A Comprehensive Roadmap for Sustainable Success</li>\\n<li>7.4 Monitoring Quality Improvement: Leveraging AI Metrics for Continuous Enhancement</li>\\n<li>7.5 Error Reporting and Safety Protocols: Ensuring Safe and Reliable AI Integration</li>\\n<li>7.6 Hands-On Activity: Calculating Clinical Risk Scores and Visualization with ChatGPT</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Capstone Project ", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. Capstone Project – Designing a Personal AI-in-Nursing Impact Plan</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FAIC_AI-Nurse.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Registered Nurses (RNs):</strong> Professionals seeking to integrate AI into daily patient care and clinical decision-making.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Nursing Students:</strong> Learners aiming to build future-ready skills in AI-driven healthcare practices.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Healthcare Administrators:</strong> Individuals looking to optimize nursing workflows and enhance patient care outcomes.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Clinical Informatics Specialists:</strong> Experts interested in applying AI to electronic health records and patient data analysis.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Nurse Educators &amp; Trainers:</strong> Professionals preparing the next generation of nurses with AI-powered healthcare knowledge.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "AI in Patient Care: ", "key_points_detail": "Learn how AI enhances patient monitoring, early warning systems, and proactive care delivery."}, {"key_points": "Clinical Decision Support: ", "key_points_detail": "Understand AI tools that assist nurses in medication management, triage, and treatment recommendations."}, {"key_points": "Workflow Optimization: ", "key_points_detail": "Discover how AI reduces administrative burdens and streamlines nursing workflows for efficiency."}, {"key_points": "Ethical and Human-Centered Care: ", "key_points_detail": "Explore responsible AI practices that preserve empathy, trust, and patient-centered values in nursing."}, {"key_points": "Practical Simulations: ", "key_points_detail": "Apply skills in real-world nursing scenarios through interactive, AI-powered case-based learning."}]}, "lms_course_id": "730", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/AIC_AI-Nurse.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/AIC_AI-Nurse.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:45:04.077157+02	2026-01-23 07:44:44.328699+02	2026-04-27 10:45:04.078776+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FAIC_AI-Nurse.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FAIC_AI-Nurse.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "Python", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Python.png"}, {"name": "Scikit-learn", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-53.jpg"}, {"name": "Keras", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Keras.png"}, {"name": "Jupyter Notebooks", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jupyter.jpg"}, {"name": "Matplotlib", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Matplotlib.png"}, {"name": "Power BI", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Power-BI.png"}]	\N	professional
1	aicerts	71563	AI+ Context Engineering™	AI+ Context Engineering™	<ul>\n<li><strong>Context Strategy &amp; Architecture:</strong> Learn how to design robust context architectures that go beyond prompts—managing instructions, memory, tools, and knowledge for reliable AI behavior across sessions and workflows.</li>\n<li><strong>Building Context-Aware AI Systems:</strong> Gain hands-on skills in implementing context pipelines, RAG architecture, and memory systems that ensure grounded, accurate, and cost-efficient AI outputs.</li>\n<li><strong>Context Management &amp; Optimization:</strong> Master the Write-Select-Compress-Isolate (W-S-C-I) framework to control relevance, reduce hallucinations, optimize token usage, and scale AI systems effectively.</li>\n<li><strong>Enterprise-Grade Context Integration:</strong> Learn how to integrate AI safely into enterprise environments with role-based access, compliance guardrails, secure memory, and conflict-free context orchestration.</li>\n<li><strong>Future-Ready Agent &amp; Workflow Design:</strong> Prepare for the next wave of AI by designing multi-agent systems, automated workflows, and context-driven architectures that remain reliable as models, tools, and scale evolve.</li>\n</ul>\n	<ul>\n<li><strong>Context Strategy &amp; Architecture:</strong> Learn how to design robust context architectures that go beyond prompts—managing instructions, memory, tools, and knowledge for reliable AI behavior across sessions and workflows.</li>\n<li><strong>Building Context-Aware AI Systems:</strong> Gain hands-on skills in implementing context pipelines, RAG architecture, and memory systems that ensure grounded, accurate, and cost-efficient AI outputs.</li>\n<li><strong>Context Management &amp; Optimization:</strong> Master the Write-Select-Compress-Isolate (W-S-C-I) framework to control relevance, reduce hallucinations, optimize token usage, and scale AI systems effectively.</li>\n<li><strong>Enterprise-Grade Context Integration:</strong> Learn how to integrate AI safely into enterprise environments with role-based access, compliance guardrails, secure memory, and conflict-free context orchestration.</li>\n<li><strong>Future-Ready Agent &amp; Workflow Design:</strong> Prepare for the next wave of AI by designing multi-agent systems, automated workflows, and context-driven architectures that remain reliable as models, tools, and scale evolve.</li>\n</ul>\n	AI Development,AI Technical,All Courses,Context Engineering Specialist,English,Language	https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/AIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg	https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/AIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg	824	t	f	260.00	f		\N	{"api_data": {"id": 71563, "title": "AI+ Context Engineering™", "categories": ["AI Development", "AI Technical", "All Courses", "Context Engineering Specialist", "English", "Language"], "description": "<ul>\\n<li><strong>Context Strategy &amp; Architecture:</strong> Learn how to design robust context architectures that go beyond prompts—managing instructions, memory, tools, and knowledge for reliable AI behavior across sessions and workflows.</li>\\n<li><strong>Building Context-Aware AI Systems:</strong> Gain hands-on skills in implementing context pipelines, RAG architecture, and memory systems that ensure grounded, accurate, and cost-efficient AI outputs.</li>\\n<li><strong>Context Management &amp; Optimization:</strong> Master the Write-Select-Compress-Isolate (W-S-C-I) framework to control relevance, reduce hallucinations, optimize token usage, and scale AI systems effectively.</li>\\n<li><strong>Enterprise-Grade Context Integration:</strong> Learn how to integrate AI safely into enterprise environments with role-based access, compliance guardrails, secure memory, and conflict-free context orchestration.</li>\\n<li><strong>Future-Ready Agent &amp; Workflow Design:</strong> Prepare for the next wave of AI by designing multi-agent systems, automated workflows, and context-driven architectures that remain reliable as models, tools, and scale evolve.</li>\\n</ul>\\n", "lms_course_id": "824", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/AIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg", "trainer_prep_course_id": "", "certificate_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F11%2FAIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg&output=jpg"}, "detail_data": {"id": 71563, "title": "AI+ Context Engineering™", "ai_tools": [{"name": "LangChain and LangGraph", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/LangChain-LangGraph.png"}, {"name": "LlamaIndex", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/LlamaIndex.png"}, {"name": "Vector Databases (Pinecone, Chroma)", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Vector-Databases-Pinecone.png"}, {"name": "n8n, Zapier, Make.com", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/n8n-Zapier-Make.com_.png"}, {"name": "Embedding Models and RAG Pipelines", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Embedding-Models-RAG-Pipelines.png"}, {"name": "No-Code Automation Platforms", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/No-Code-Automation-Platforms.png"}, {"name": "Enterprise Data and API Integrations", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Enterprise-Data-API-Integrations.png"}], "description": "<ul>\\n<li><strong>Context Strategy &amp; Architecture:</strong> Learn how to design robust context architectures that go beyond prompts—managing instructions, memory, tools, and knowledge for reliable AI behavior across sessions and workflows.</li>\\n<li><strong>Building Context-Aware AI Systems:</strong> Gain hands-on skills in implementing context pipelines, RAG architecture, and memory systems that ensure grounded, accurate, and cost-efficient AI outputs.</li>\\n<li><strong>Context Management &amp; Optimization:</strong> Master the Write-Select-Compress-Isolate (W-S-C-I) framework to control relevance, reduce hallucinations, optimize token usage, and scale AI systems effectively.</li>\\n<li><strong>Enterprise-Grade Context Integration:</strong> Learn how to integrate AI safely into enterprise environments with role-based access, compliance guardrails, secure memory, and conflict-free context orchestration.</li>\\n<li><strong>Future-Ready Agent &amp; Workflow Design:</strong> Prepare for the next wave of AI by designing multi-agent systems, automated workflows, and context-driven architectures that remain reliable as models, tools, and scale evolve.</li>\\n</ul>\\n", "lms_course_id": "824", "course_tagline": "Master AI+ Context Engineering for Production-Grade AI Systems", "certificate_code": "AP 3309", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/AIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg", "certificate_overview": {"exam_format": "50 questions, 70% passing, 90 minutes, online proctored exam ", "prerequisites": "A solid foundation in AI and machine learning concepts, proficiency in programming and data handling, familiarity with cloud platforms and IoT environments, and the ability to design, manage, and optimize contextual data, memory, and tool orchestration are essential for this course. ", "included_items": "Instructor-led OR Self-paced course + Official exam + Digital badge ", "certificate_duration": "<ul>\\n<li>Instructor-Led: 1 day (live or virtual)</li>\\n<li>Self-Paced: 8 hours of content</li>\\n</ul>\\n"}, "certification_modules": [{"certification_module_title": "Module 1: Foundations of Context Engineering – Introduction", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1.1 What is Context Engineering (Beyond Prompt Engineering)</li>\\n<li>1.2 From Prompting to Context Pipelines: The 2025 Paradigm Shift</li>\\n<li>1.3 The Four Building Blocks of Context: Instructions, Knowledge, Tools, State</li>\\n<li>1.4 Short-Term vs Long-Term Memory in LLM Systems</li>\\n<li>1.5 Benefits of Context Engineering: Grounding, Relevance, Continuity, Cost Control</li>\\n<li>1.6 Use Case: Context-Aware AI Travel Assistant</li>\\n<li>1.7 Hands-on: Designing System Instructions and Memory State for a Role-Based AI Agent</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: Context Management Patterns & Techniques", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>2.1 The W-S-C-I Framework: Write, Select, Compress, Isolate</li>\\n<li>2.2 WRITE Strategy: Agent Identity, Persona, Guardrails, and State</li>\\n<li>2.3 SELECT Strategy: Precision Retrieval &amp; Metadata Filtering</li>\\n<li>2.4 COMPRESS Strategy: Summarization, Token Optimization, Auto-Compaction</li>\\n<li>2.5 ISOLATE Strategy: Context Boundaries, Safety, and Focus</li>\\n<li>2.6 Advanced Retrieval Patterns: Hybrid Search, Semantic Chunking</li>\\n<li>2.7 Case Study: ChatGPT &amp; Claude Memory Systems</li>\\n<li>2.8 Hands-on: Implement Context Selection &amp; Compression Using LangChain / LlamaIndex</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: Context Pipelines, RAG & Grounding Architecture", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>3.1 The End-to-End Context Pipeline (Input → Retrieval → Compression → Assembly → Response → Update)</li>\\n<li>3.2 Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) Architecture Deep Dive</li>\\n<li>3.3 Vector Databases: Pinecone, Chroma &amp; Embedding Models</li>\\n<li>3.4 Grounding Failures: Hallucinations, Context Poisoning, Distraction</li>\\n<li>3.5 Mitigation Techniques: Rerankers, Provenance, Context Forensics</li>\\n<li>3.6 Case Study: Anthropic’s Multi-Agent Researcher (MAR)</li>\\n<li>3.7 Hands-on: Build a RAG Pipeline with Vector Search and Grounded Responses</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: Optimization, Scaling & Enterprise Readiness", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 Token Economy &amp; Cost Optimization in Context Pipelines</li>\\n<li>4.2 Context Scaling &amp; the Model Context Protocol (MCP)</li>\\n<li>4.3 Security &amp; Compliance: PII Filtering, Redaction, Role-Based Access</li>\\n<li>4.4 Conflict Resolution &amp; Context Consistency</li>\\n<li>4.5 Multi-Modal Context: Text, Tables, PDFs, Video Transcripts</li>\\n<li>4.6 Case Studies: Walmart “Ask Sam” &amp; Morgan Stanley Knowledge Assistant</li>\\n<li>4.7 Hands-on: Implement Role-Based Context Filtering and Secure Retrieval</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Context Flow Design for Business Users (No-Code AI)", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Translating Business Processes into AI-Ready Context Flows</li>\\n<li>5.2 Context Flow Diagrams (CFDs) &amp; Automated Workflow Architecture (AWA)</li>\\n<li>5.3 Implementing W-S-C-I Visually Using No-Code Tools (n8n / Make / Zapier)</li>\\n<li>5.4 Context Templates for Consistency &amp; Structured Outputs</li>\\n<li>5.5 Use Case: Dynamic Customer Onboarding Assistant</li>\\n<li>5.6 Case Studies: Airbnb Support Automation &amp; HSBC SME Lending</li>\\n<li>5.7 Hands-on: Build a Context Flow Using No-Code Orchestration</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Real-World Industry Context Applications", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Context Engineering in Regulated Domains</li>\\n<li>6.2 Healthcare: Clinical Decision Support &amp; PHI Isolation</li>\\n<li>6.3 Finance: Market Analysis, Compliance Summarization &amp; Tool-Based Context</li>\\n<li>6.4 Legal &amp; Education: Precision Retrieval &amp; Personalized Learning Context</li>\\n<li>6.5 Risk Mitigation: Context Poisoning &amp; Context Clash</li>\\n<li>6.6 Advanced Agent Memory for Long-Horizon Tasks</li>\\n<li>6.7 Case Studies: Activeloop (Legal/IP) &amp; Five Sigma (Insurance)</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Multi-Agent Orchestration & the Future", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Why Monolithic Agents Fail: Context Explosion</li>\\n<li>7.2 Multi-Agent Systems (MAS) &amp; Context Isolation</li>\\n<li>7.3 Agent Roles: Router, Planner, Executor</li>\\n<li>7.4 Agent-to-Agent Context Compression</li>\\n<li>7.5 Guardrails, Governance &amp; Inter-Agent Safety</li>\\n<li>7.6 Ethics, Bias Mitigation &amp; Source Traceability</li>\\n<li>7.7 Case Studies: IBM Watson Orchestrate &amp; Enterprise Context Orchestrators</li>\\n<li>7.8 Career Pathways: Context Architect &amp; AI Governance Roles</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Capstone Project & Certification", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Capstone Overview: Multi-Agent Context-Aware System</li>\\n<li>8.2 Build: Query Router with Financial Calculations &amp; Policy RAG (n8n)</li>\\n<li>8.3 Presentation, Review &amp; Feedback</li>\\n<li>8.4 Final Evaluation &amp; AI+ Context Engineering Certification</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F11%2FAIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>AI Engineers &amp; LLM Developers:</strong> Built for practitioners who want to move beyond basic prompt engineering and design production-grade, context-aware AI systems using RAG, memory, tools, and orchestration patterns</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Product Managers &amp; AI Architects:</strong> Ideal for professionals responsible for shipping reliable AI features who need to understand context pipelines, grounding, cost control, and system-level design tradeoffs rather than toy demos</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Data &amp; Platform Engineers:</strong> For engineers working with vector databases, embeddings, retrieval systems, and AI infrastructure who want to architect scalable, efficient, and trustworthy context flows</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Enterprise &amp; Solution Architects:</strong> Designed for architects building AI systems in regulated or large-scale environments who must manage security, compliance, cost optimization, and multi-agent orchestration</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>AI Consultants &amp; Technical Leaders:</strong> For professionals advising organizations on AI adoption who need a deep, practical understanding of why context—not just models—is the real differentiator in modern AI systems</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Advanced No-Code / Automation Builders:</strong> A strong fit for builders using tools like n8n, Make, or Zapier who want to design reliable AI workflows and agentic systems without writing heavy infrastructure code</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Go beyond prompts", "key_points_detail": "Learn to engineer instructions, tools, memory, and state so AI behaves reliably. "}, {"key_points": "Production-ready systems", "key_points_detail": "Build RAG + context pipelines that reduce hallucinations and improve grounding. "}, {"key_points": "Scale with efficiency", "key_points_detail": "Master selection + compression to control token cost, latency, and performance. "}, {"key_points": "Enterprise-safe AI", "key_points_detail": "Apply PII controls, role-based filtering, and conflict resolution for compliant deployments. "}, {"key_points": "Real deliverable", "key_points_detail": "Complete a multi-agent capstone (n8n) with routing + calculations + policy RAG. "}]}, "lms_course_id": "824", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/AIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/AIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:44:23.795154+02	2026-01-23 07:44:16.997173+02	2026-04-27 10:44:23.796617+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F11%2FAIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F11%2FAIC_AI-Context-Engineering.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "LangChain and LangGraph", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/LangChain-LangGraph.png"}, {"name": "LlamaIndex", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/LlamaIndex.png"}, {"name": "Vector Databases (Pinecone, Chroma)", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Vector-Databases-Pinecone.png"}, {"name": "n8n, Zapier, Make.com", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/n8n-Zapier-Make.com_.png"}, {"name": "Embedding Models and RAG Pipelines", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Embedding-Models-RAG-Pipelines.png"}, {"name": "No-Code Automation Platforms", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/No-Code-Automation-Platforms.png"}, {"name": "Enterprise Data and API Integrations", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Enterprise-Data-API-Integrations.png"}]	\N	technical
