ucation</li>\\n<li>6.3 Data-Driven Decision Making</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: AI-Enhanced Assessment and Feedback", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>7.1 Revolutionizing Assessments</li>\\n<li>7.2 Automated Grading Systems</li>\\n<li>7.3 Personalized Learning Paths</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: AI Tools and Hands-on Experience", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Exploring AI Tools</li>\\n<li>8.2 Practical Exercises</li>\\n<li>8.3 Evaluating AI Tool Effectiveness</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Education", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. Understanding AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Case Studies</li>\\n<li>3. Hands-On Practice with AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Educator.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong><span class=\\"TextRun SCXW191054166 BCX8\\" lang=\\"EN-US\\" xml:lang=\\"EN-US\\" data-contrast=\\"auto\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXW191054166 BCX8\\">Data Scientists</span></span></strong><span class=\\"TextRun SCXW191054166 BCX8\\" lang=\\"EN-US\\" xml:lang=\\"EN-US\\" data-contrast=\\"auto\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXW191054166 BCX8\\"><strong>:</strong> Use AI and quantum computing to analyze and interpret complex datasets.</span></span><span class=\\"EOP SCXW191054166 BCX8\\" data-ccp-props=\\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:278}\\"> </span></p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong><span class=\\"TextRun SCXW27577983 BCX8\\" lang=\\"EN-US\\" xml:lang=\\"EN-US\\" data-contrast=\\"auto\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXW27577983 BCX8\\">Software Developers</span></span></strong><