le 5: Deep Learning", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Neural Networks</li>\\n<li>5.2 Improving Model Performance</li>\\n<li>5.3 Hands-on: Evaluating and Optimizing AI Models</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Computer Vision", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Image Processing Basics</li>\\n<li>6.2 Object Detection</li>\\n<li>6.3 Image Segmentation</li>\\n<li>6.4 Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs)</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Natural Language Processing", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Text Preprocessing and Representation</li>\\n<li>7.2 Text Classification</li>\\n<li>7.3 Named Entity Recognition (NER)</li>\\n<li>7.4 Question Answering (QA)</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: Reinforcement Learning", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Introduction to Reinforcement Learning</li>\\n<li>8.2 Q-Learning and Deep Q-Networks (DQNs)</li>\\n<li>8.3 Policy Gradient Methods</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 9: Cloud Computing in AI Development", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>9.1 Cloud Computing for AI</li>\\n<li>9.2 Cloud-Based Machine Learning Services</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 10: Large Language Models", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>10.1 Understanding LLMs</li>\\n<li>10.2 Text Generation and Translation</li>\\n<li>10.3 Question Answering and Knowledge Extraction</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 11: Cutting-Edge AI Research", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>11.1 Neuro-Symbolic AI</li>\\n<li>11.2 Explainable AI (XAI)</li>\\n<li>11.3 Federated Learning</li>\\n<li>11.4 Meta-Learning and Few-Shot Learning</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 12: AI Communication and Documentation", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>12.1 Communicating AI Projects</li>\\n<li>12.2 Documenting AI Systems</li>\\n<li>12.3 Ethical Considerations</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Developers", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. Understanding AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Case Studies</li>\\n<li>3. Hands-On Practice with AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Developer.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Software Developers</strong><strong>:</strong> Enhance your coding expertise by mastering AI algorithms and deep learning techniques.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Data Enthusiasts</strong><strong>:</strong> Apply AI-driven data analysis, machine learning models, and deep learning to solve complex problems.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Computer Vision &amp; NLP Researchers</strong><strong>:</strong> Dive into specialized AI fields, including computer vision and natural language processing.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>IT Specialists &amp; System Architects</strong><strong>:</strong> Integrate AI solutions into existing systems and optimize performance.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong>Students &amp; Fresh Graduates</strong><strong>:</strong> Build a strong foundation in AI development and prepare for future opportunities in tech.</p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Master Key AI Development Skills:", "key_points_detail": "Learn Python, deep learning, advanced concepts, and optimization techniques to build robust AI solutions. "}, {"key_points": "Specialize in Cutting-Edge AI Domains:", "key_points_detail": "Gain expertise in NLP, computer vision, or reinforcement learning, alongside data processing, exploratory analysis, and time series analysis. "}, {"key_points": "Stay Ahead in AI Development:", "key_points_detail": "AI is transforming industries, and organizations seek developers with strong proficiency in deploying AI models to solve real-world problems. "}, {"key_points": "Advance Your Career in AI Development:", "key_points_detail": "With growing demand across tech, finance, and healthcare sectors, this certification positions you as a leader in AI-driven development. "}]}, "lms_course_id": "511", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Developer.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AIC_AI-Developer.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:45:44.789951+02	2026-01-23 07:45:12.330717+02	2026-04-27 10:45:44.791507+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Developer.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAIC_AI-Developer.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "GitHub Copilot", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-34.jpg"}, {"name": "Lobe", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-35.jpg"}, {"name": "H2O.ai", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-36.jpg"}, {"name": "Snorkel", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-37.jpg"}]	\N	technical
