erview", "certification_module_description": "<ol class=\\"faq-list-title\\">\\n<li>Course Introduction <a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HWE6Ko8q0HQ\\">Preview </a></li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 1: Introduction to Bitcoin", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1.1 Deep Dive into Bitcoin&#8217;s Nature</li>\\n<li>1.2 The Genesis of Bitcoin</li>\\n<li>1.3 Technical Foundations of Bitcoin</li>\\n<li>1.4 Comparing Bitcoin with Traditional Financial Systems</li>\\n<li>1.5 Societal Implications of Bitcoin</li>\\n<li>1.6 Case Studies</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: How Bitcoin Works?", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>2.1 Blockchain Technology</li>\\n<li>2.2 Bitcoin Transactions</li>\\n<li>2.3 Mining and Consensus</li>\\n<li>2.4 Network Nodes</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: Setting Up a Bitcoin Wallet", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>3.1 Introduction to Bitcoin Wallets</li>\\n<li>3.2 Setting Up Your First Wallet</li>\\n<li>3.3 Securing Your Wallet</li>\\n<li>3.4 Receiving and Sending Bitcoin</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: Buying, Selling, and Using Bitcoin", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 Acquiring Bitcoin</li>\\n<li>4.2 Using Bitcoin for Transactions</li>\\n<li>4.3 Selling and Converting Bitcoin</li>\\n<li>4.4 Staying Informed and Secure</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: Bitcoin Security", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Fundamentals of Cryptocurrency Security</li>\\n<li>5.2 Advanced Wallet Security</li>\\n<li>5.3 Recognizing and Avoiding Scams</li>\\n<li>5.4 Operational Security (OpSec) for Bitcoin</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Bitcoin's Economic Aspects", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Bitcoin&#8217;s Monetary Policy</li>\\n<li>6.2 Bitcoin and the Global Economy</li>\\n<li>6.3 Investing in Bitcoin</li>\\n<li>6.4 Market Analysis and Speculation</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Legal and Regulatory Environment", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Bitcoin&#8217;s Legal Status Worldwide</li>\\n<li>7.2 Regulatory Frameworks for Cryptocurrencies</li>\\n<li>7.3 Taxation of Bitcoin</li>\\n<li>7.4 Navigating the Regulatory Landscape</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 8: The Future of Bitcoin", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>8.1 Technological Advances</li>\\n<li>8.2 Bitcoin&#8217;s Adoption and Integration</li>\\n<li>8.3 Economic and Societal Impacts</li>\\n<li>8.4 Speculations on the Future</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAIC_Bitcoin-Everyone.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong><span class=\\"TextRun SCXW53112464 BCX0\\" lang=\\"EN-US\\" xml:lang=\\"EN-US\\" data-contrast=\\"auto\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXW53112464 BCX0\\">Business Leaders, Managers, and Executives</span></span></strong><span class=\\"TextRun SCXW53112464 BCX0\\" lang=\\"EN-US\\" xml:lang=\\"EN-US\\" data-contrast=\\"auto\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXW53112464 BCX0\\"><strong>:</strong> Leaders determined to harness Bitcoin to enhance business strategies and operations. </span></span><span class=\\"EOP SCXW53112464 BCX0\\" data-ccp-props=\\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:278}\\"> </span></p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p><strong><span class=\\"TextRun SCXW4316410 BCX0\\" lang=\\"EN-US\\" xml:lang=\\"EN-US\\" data-contrast=\\"auto\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXW4316410 BCX0\\">Financial Professionals</span></span></strong><span class=\\"TextRun SCXW4316410 BCX0\\" lang=\\"EN-US\\" xml:lang=\\"EN-US\\" data-contrast=\\"auto\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXW4316410 BCX0\\"><strong>:</strong> Finance experts focused