8217;s technical details and applications.</span></span><span class=\\"EOP SCXW6983325 BCX0\\" data-ccp-props=\\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:278}\\"> </span></p>\\n"}], "why_this_certification_matters": [{"key_points": "Comprehensive Understanding of Bitcoin: ", "key_points_detail": "Gain a thorough grasp of Bitcoin’s history, technology, and its global impact on financial systems. "}, {"key_points": "Master Bitcoin Transaction Mechanics:", "key_points_detail": "Learn the mechanics of Bitcoin transactions and explore security best practices to protect your assets. "}, {"key_points": "Explore Economic and Regulatory Implications: ", "key_points_detail": "Understand the economic implications and regulatory environments shaping the future of Bitcoin. "}, {"key_points": "Practical Insights for Real-World Applications: ", "key_points_detail": "Equip yourself with practical knowledge to apply Bitcoin in real-world scenarios across various industries. "}, {"key_points": "Build a Strong Blockchain Foundation: ", "key_points_detail": "Strengthen your understanding of blockchain technology to navigate the evolving cryptocurrency landscape confidently. "}]}, "lms_course_id": "65", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/AIC_Bitcoin-Everyone.svg", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/AIC_Bitcoin-Everyone.svg"}	2026-04-27 10:45:35.130685+02	2026-01-23 07:45:05.807786+02	2026-04-27 10:45:35.13311+02	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAIC_Bitcoin-Everyone.svg&output=jpg	https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAIC_Bitcoin-Everyone.svg&output=jpg	[{"name": "99Bitcoins", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img-5.png"}, {"name": "BlockCypher", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-45.png"}, {"name": "Bitcoin Dev Kit (BDK)", "tool_image": 