36	aicerts	14798	AI+ Network™	AI+ Network™	<p>This course provides professionals with the basic knowledge and advanced skills needed to understand the combination of artificial intelligence and current networking technologies. It discusses fundamental networking concepts, newer technologies such as SDN and NFV, and how AI can enhance network efficiency. Important focus areas consist of AI-powered network automation, orchestration, and security upgrades, combined with hands-on projects and practical labs for real-life implementation. The class ends by examining new developments and<br />\nupcoming pathways in AI-enhanced networking, getting students ready for leading positions in this quickly changing sector.</p>\n	<p>This course provides professionals with the basic knowledge and advanced skills needed to understand the combination of artificial intelligence and current networking technologies. It discusses fundamental networking concepts, newer technologies such as SDN and NFV, and how AI can enhance network efficiency. Important focus areas consist of AI-powered network automation, orchestration, and security upgrades, combined with hands-on projects and practical labs for real-life implementation. The class ends by examining new developments and<br />\nupcoming pathways in AI-enhanced networking, getting students ready for leading positions in this quickly changing sector.</p>\n	AI Security,AI Technical,All Courses,DevOps Engineer,English,Language,Network Security Engineer,Spanish,Telecommunications Specialist	https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/AIC_AI-Network.svg	https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/AIC_AI-Network.svg	497	t	f	260.00	f		\N	{"api_data": {"id": 14798, "title": "AI+ Network™", "categories": ["AI Security", "AI Technical", "All Courses", "DevOps Engineer", "English", "Language", "Network Security Engineer", "Spanish", "Telecommunications Specialist"], "description": "<p>This course provides professionals with the basic knowledge and advanced skills needed to understand the combination of artificial intelligence and current networking technologies. It discusses fundamental networking concepts, newer technologies such as SDN and NFV, and how AI can enhance network efficiency. Important focus areas consist of AI-powered network automation, orchestration, and security upgrades, combined with hands-on projects and practical labs for real-life implementation. The class ends by examining new developments and<br />\\nupcoming pathways in AI-enhanced networking, getting students ready for leading positions in this quickly changing sector.</p>\\n", "lms_course_id": "497", "certificate_badge_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/AIC_AI-Network.svg", "trainer_prep_course_id": "", "certificate_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAIC_AI-Network.svg&output=jpg"}, "detail_data": {"id": 14798, "title": "AI+ Network™", "ai_tools": [{"name": "Elastic", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-13-2.jpg"}, {"name": "Juniper", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Frame-886-4-2.jpg"}, {"name": "Netdata", "tool_image": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-4-1.jpg"}], "description": "<p>This course provides professionals with the basic knowledge and advanced skills needed to understand the combination of artificial intelligence and current networking technologies. It discusses fundamental networking concepts, newer technologies such as SDN and NFV, and how AI can enhance network efficiency. Important focus areas consist of AI-powered network automation, orchestration, and security upgrades, combined with hands-on projects and practical labs for real-life implementation. The class ends by examining new developments and<br />\\nupcoming pathways in AI-enhanced networking, getting students ready for leading positions in this quickly changing sector.</p>\\n", "lms_course_id": "497", "course_tagline": "Master the Future of Networking: Harness AI for Automation, Security, and Next-Generation Efficiency ", "certificate_code": "AT-510", "feature_image_url": "https://www.aicerts.ai/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/AIC_AI-Network.svg", "certificate_overview": {"exam_format": "50 questions, 70% passing, 90 minutes, online proctored exam ", "prerequisites": "Basic networking knowledge, Python familiarity, fundamental AI/ML concepts, Experience with network management tools is a plus ", "included_items": "Instructor-led OR Self-paced course + Official exam + Digital badge ", "certificate_duration": "<p>• Instructor-Led: 5 Days (live or virtual)</p>\\n<p>• Self-Paced: 40 hours of content</p>\\n"}, "certification_modules": [{"certification_module_title": "Module 1: Networking Foundations", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1.1 Basic Networking Concepts</li>\\n<li>1.2 Networking Protocols and Standards</li>\\n<li>1.3 Network Infrastructure and Design</li>\\n<li>1.4 Introduction to Network Security</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 2: Advanced Networking Technologies", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>2.1 Network Virtualization and Cloud Networking</li>\\n<li>2.2 Emerging Network Architectures</li>\\n<li>2.3 Advanced Routing and Switching</li>\\n<li>2.4 Network Storage and Data Centers</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 3: AI in Networking", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>3.1 Introduction to AI and Machine Learning</li>\\n<li>3.2 AI-Driven Network Optimization</li>\\n<li>3.3 AI for Network Security and Threat Detection</li>\\n<li>3.4 AI-Enhanced Network Management</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 4: Network Automation and Orchestration", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>4.1 Fundamentals of Network Automation</li>\\n<li>4.2 AI-Driven Network Orchestration</li>\\n<li>4.3 Policy-Driven Network Management</li>\\n<li>4.4 Case Studies in Network Automation</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 5: AI-Enhanced Network Security", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>5.1 Advanced Threat Detection with AI</li>\\n<li>5.2 Secure Network Design and Architecture</li>\\n<li>5.3 AI for Cybersecurity Intelligence</li>\\n<li>5.4 Ethical Considerations in AI-Driven Security</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 6: Practical Labs and Hands-On Projects", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>6.1 Network Simulation and Emulation</li>\\n<li>6.2 AI-Driven Network Automation Projects</li>\\n<li>6.3 AI for Network Security Projects</li>\\n<li>6.4 Capstone Project (Using Google Colab and Azure cloud)</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Module 7: Emerging Trends and Future Directions", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>7.1 Future of AI in Networking</li>\\n<li>7.2 AI-Powered IoT Networks</li>\\n<li>7.3 Blockchain and AI in Networking</li>\\n<li>7.4 Continuous Learning and Career Development</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}, {"certification_module_title": "Optional Module: AI Agents for Network Management", "certification_module_description": "<ol>\\n<li>1. Understanding AI Agents</li>\\n<li>2. Case Studies</li>\\n<li>3. Hands-On Practice with AI Agents</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}], "feature_image_jpg_url": "https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aicerts.ai%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAIC_AI-Network.svg&output=jpg", "who_should_enroll_points": [{"who_should_enroll_point": "<p>Networking Professionals: Modernize your skill set by integrating AI for automation and optimization.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p>AI Enthusiasts: Interested in applying AI technologies like ML and automation specifically to networking domains.</p>\\n"}, {"who_should_enroll_point": "<p>IT Specialists: Focused on exploring the intersection of cloud computing, IoT, and AI to optimize infrastructure and network performance.</p>\\n"}, {"